## Project structure

```
rgsupervision/
├── setup.php                  ← Plugin declaration and GLPI hooks
├── hook.php                   ← Install / uninstall (database tables)
├── inc/
│   ├── config.class.php       ← Read/write configuration from database
│   ├── rgapiclient.class.php  ← cURL client for the RG Supervision API
│   ├── sync.class.php         ← Synchronization logic + cron entry point
│   └── syncstate.class.php    ← Sync state management in database
└── front/
    ├── config.php             ← Configuration page
    └── config.form.php        ← Form processing
```

### Database tables created on installation

| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `glpi_plugin_rgsupervision_configs` | Key/value configuration |
| `glpi_plugin_rgsupervision_syncs` | Synchronization state (replaces the JSON file) |
| `glpi_plugin_rgsupervision_logs` | Run history |

